---
title: Brazilian-Style Steak with Shrimp Stew plus Chimichurri, Rice & Roasted Broccoli
description: This bountiful Brazilian-style meal isn’t your usual surf-n-turf. Alongside juicy seared steak drizzled with herby chimichurri, you’ll serve a shrimp stew inspired by moqueca—a Brazilian seafood stew made with bell peppers, cilantro, and coconut milk. A bed of white rice and a side of roasted broccoli complete this hearty, satisfying dish.
